    <item name="Astrin Grav APC">
        <category>Vehicle</category>
        <genre>Traveller</genre>
        <techLevel>12</techLevel>
        <legality>1</legality>
        <availability>1</availability>
        <importance>3</importance>

        <short>Heavy APC for moving troops to the front line.</short>

        <cost units="Cr">1200000</cost>
        <mass>15500000</mass>

        <construction>
            <year>1030</year>
            <manufacturer>Vilani</manufacturer>
        </construction>

        <performance realm="Air">
            <speed>1000</speed>
            <acceleration>90</acceleration>
            <altitude>50000</altitude>
            <range>3500</range>
        </performance>

        <description>
            <para>
                This contra-grav APC is the mainstay of troop deployment in
                the Imperium's army. Though it can't stand up to a modern
                tank, it is armed and armoured enough to defend itself against
                most infantry weapons, and most things low tech armies can
                throw at it.
            </para>

            <para>
                It has 3 crew (driver, gunner and commander) and up to 10
                passengers in heavy combat armour.
            </para>
        </description>

